---
const homeHref = '/';
const serviceHref = '/service/';
const adsHref = '/landing-page-ads/';
const blogHref = '/blog/';
const contactHref = '/contact/';
const privacyHref = '/privacy/';
---
<footer class="bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-8 max-w-screen-xl">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">my-aicustom.com</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-500">Otomatisasi bisnis Anda dengan solusi AI terdepan.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">Navigasi</h3>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2">
          <li><a href={homeHref} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-500">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href={serviceHref} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-500">Service</a></li>
          <li><a href={adsHref} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-500">Landing Ads</a></li>
          <li><a href={blogHref} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-500">Blog</a></li>
          <li><a href={contactHref} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-500">Konsultasi Gratis</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">Butuh Bantuan?</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-500">Tim kami siap berdiskusi dan memberikan rekomendasi terbaik.</p>
        <a href={contactHref} class="inline-flex items-center justify-center mt-4 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-blue-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-gray-50:ring-offset-gray-800">Hubungi Tim Kami</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 border-t border-gray-200 pt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3">
      <p class="text-gray-500">&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} my-aicustom.com. All rights reserved.</p>
      <a href={privacyHref} class="text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-blue-500">Privacy Policy</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
